data.description: Welcome to this impeccably maintained, like-new townhome nestled in the serene cul-de-sac of the highly sought-after Fairington Township community. Boasting three bedrooms and two and one-half bathrooms, this all-electric residence offers a perfect blend of modern convenience and timeless elegance. As you step through the front door, you are greeted by a spacious formal dining room on your right, seamlessly flowing into the well-appointed kitchen. The kitchen is equipped with a convenient breakfast bar, sleek black appliances, a pantry, and offers picturesque views to the inviting living room. The main level also features a convenient half bath, ensuring practicality for both residents and guests, and grants access to the back patio. Enjoy the tranquility of your private outdoor space, as it backs up to a wooded area, providing an oasis of privacy. Venturing upstairs, discover the primary bedroom that exudes comfort and luxury, complete with a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom featuring a double vanity. Two additional generously sized secondary bedrooms share a well-appointed hallway bathroom. For added convenience, a dedicated laundry room completes the upper level, streamlining your daily routine. The Fairington Township community is strategically located, offering easy access to major thoroughfares such as I-20 and I-285. This prime location ensures a swift commute and places you in close proximity to shopping centers, a variety of dining options, and MARTA for effortless travel. Whether you're an investor seeking a lucrative opportunity or a first-time home buyer ready to embark on the journey of homeownership, this property is the perfect choice. Don't miss the chance to experience the charm and convenience this townhome has to offer. Schedule you're showing today and make this exceptional property your next home!
